  <summary>11/4/2003--Introduced.
Foam Fire Safety Act - Directs the Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC) to promulgate safety standards that address open flame ignition of mattresses, bedding, upholstered furniture, and sound proofing materials, and other materials containing polyurethane.</summary>
